apter-strength contributions. The HIGH findings are gaps in the architectural specification that the prose elsewhere in the recipe correctly diagnoses; closing them brings the architecture up to the standard the recipe text claims and makes the recipe's defining claim ("the architecture is then load-bearing for compliance and for patient dignity in the same operational layer, which is the right place for both") fully realized.[K
